title: Power AirFryer XL Testimonial
description:
Do you love fried food? Lauren does, but couldn’t stand the oily, greasy mess it made. That’s when she found the Power Air Fryer XL. Now, she places her food into the basket & the rest is 1-touch easy. The superheated air does the frying without oil and grease. No more soaking & scrubbing afterwards!

Frying your favorite foods has never been easier with the Power Air Fryer XL. It’s virtually goof-proof. Simply add your food to the Easy Load basket, slide it into the unit, and with the touch of a finger select your cooking setting from one of the 7 preset programs. The digital touch panel display eliminates the guesswork and ensures whatever you're cooking comes out perfectly delicious time after time. 

It does all the thinking for you, and when the timer is done, the automatic shut-off stops the cooking cycle so you never overcook or burn your meal. You’ll love the versatility of this 6 in 1 kitchen wonder. It Air Fries, Bakes, Steams, Sautes, Grills and Roasts. The amazing turbo-cyclonic super heated air powered by 1500 watts reaches up to 400 degrees in a matter of seconds. 

Choose from our 5.3 quart or 3.4 quart model. Now you can enjoy fried foods without the guilt with the Power Air Fryer XL.

transcripts: I love the power air fryer because I love fried foods all kinds of fried foods, but it can be such a pain to fry your foods and also everyone's always telling you they're unhealthy, fried foods are bad for you, but now that I found the power airfryer it has made a huge difference. First of all, the cooking is so easy to do. There's two compartments that I can use. It's not messy; the cleanup doesn't take hours. I just put in my favorite food which is fried chicken and it's ready. You know the power airfryer also steams, it's sautés, it roasts, and of course it fries. Who would think that a fryer could do all of these things and that the food could taste so good and be so much healthier for you. And you don't have all the mess in the cleanup the power airfryer has done a world of good for me and my family and in my kitchen and allowed me to do so many of the things that took so long to do. I can do it all in the power air fryer.
